headline: Alphabet Inc. (GOOG) Q2 Earnings and Revenues Top Estimates
summary: Alphabet (GOOG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +138.14% and +2.82%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: July 2025's Noteworthy Stocks Trading Below Estimated Fair Value
summary: The United States market has shown a robust performance, with a 1.3% increase over the last week and a 15% rise over the past year, while earnings are projected to grow by 15% annually in the coming years. In this environment, identifying stocks that are trading below their estimated fair value can present opportunities for investors seeking to capitalize on potential growth at an attractive price point.
